## Changes made

This dataset has been **restructured** from its original Open Context form:
records were modeled into a relational PostgreSQL / PostGIS schema, point
geometry was generated in EPSG:4326, and a denormalized analysis layer
(`public.finds`, `public.sites`) was derived from the source records. No
underlying archaeological observations were altered.
